      "patchset_number": 2,
      "message": "RE IT-26214: I believe you may need to add `graphviz` to the pip requirements for this build. In truth, I'm not entirely certain about that; the documentation for it is quite bad, and it's hard to tell why this is suddenly occurring now. But in addition to the one syntax error I pointed out, this is the first thing we should try when getting an error that says the job is missing some required package.",
